text: Dr. Jyoti Jayant Gogte (born 26 March 1956) is an Indian author, most notable for her 2014 academic reference guide Start Up & New Venture Management. She holds a PhD in Finance from the University of Pune. She is a former president of the Women's Cricket Association of India and Netball Federation of India. She has received the Udyog Chakra award from the Mahratta Chamber of Commerce, Industries and Agriculture. == List of works == * Start Up & New Venture Management (2014) == References == Category:20th-century Indian writers Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Marathi people
